title: Design Autonomous Vehicle Architecture
description: Create a high-level design for the autonomous vehicles in urban environments.

title: Develop Urban Mapping System
description: Create a mapping system for urban environments that enables autonomous vehicles to navigate safely.

title: Implement Autonomous Driving Algorithms
description: Develop algorithms for the vehicles to navigate and make decisions autonomously.

title: Develop User Interface for Vehicles and Management System
description: Create a user interface for controlling the vehicles and managing the fleet.

title: Test and Validate Autonomous Vehicles
description: Conduct thorough testing and validation of the autonomous vehicles in controlled environments.

title: Deploy Fleet of Autonomous Vehicles in Controlled Environment
description: Prepare for and execute the deployment of a fleet of autonomous vehicles in a controlled urban environment.

title: Analyze Fleet Performance Data
description: Analyze data collected from the deployed fleet to identify any issues or areas for improvement.
dependencies: Deploy Fleet of Autonomous Vehicles in Controlled Environment

title: Address Security Concerns
description: Implement necessary security measures to ensure the safety and privacy of users and autonomous vehicles.
dependencies: Deploy Fleet of Autonomous Vehicles in Controlled Environment
